I got their shampoo/body wash and conditioner. Their products are amazing and I love the natural ingredients! Lotion is very hydrating for kids skin and has a nice scent. Quick absorbing and leaves skin feeling very soft and smooth. Definitely recommend! Review Title: Great natural lotion for kids Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Large Silk Scrunchies For Hair - Tara Sartoria Artisan Handmade Review Date: 2022/01/05 Store: Tara Sartoria Average Rating: 4.5 Product Details: {'Material': 'Silk', 'Item Form': 'Scrunchie', 'Brand': 'Tara Sartoria', 'Hair Type': 'Straight', 'Number of Pieces': '1', 'Package Dimensions': '4.37 x 3.9 x 0.71 inches; 1.09 Ounces'} Review Text: These are very beautiful and feel really nice. Oz. Travel Packs Review Date: 2022/02/26 Store: AllWell AllOver Average Rating: 4.3 Product Details: {'Brand': 'AllWell AllOver', 'Product Benefits': 'Moisturizing', 'Scent': 'Lavender', 'Material Type Free': 'Phthalates', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Package Dimensions': '6.26 x 2.6 x 1.06 inches; 3.84 Ounces', 'UPC': '850012824268'} Review Text: This mask has helped my skin feel soo soft and smooth. It does an excellent job hydrating the skin that it feels so nice. I love that it comes in individual packets as it makes it easier for travel. It also doesn't have funky smell like others I have tried in past, this is important to me. I definitely would recommend! Review Title: Love it! Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Solflower SPF 30 Sunscreen Lotion - Broad Spectrum, UVA/UVB Protection - PABA-Free, Oil-Free - 3.36 Fl Oz Review Date: 2022/03/13 Store: Solflower Average Rating: 4.4 Product Details: {'Scent': 'Aloe Vera', 'Sun Protection Factor': '30 Sun Protection Factor (SPF)', 'Unit Count': '3.36 Fl Oz', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Brand': 'Solflower', 'Package Dimensions': '5.08 x 1.93 x 1.89 inches; 5.93 Ounces', 'Item model number': '860006763404', 'UPC': '860006763404'} Review Text: Very light sunscreen lotion that goes on smooth and absorbs quickly. Doesn't make my face oily which I like or leave a white cast. Good under makeup as well. Definitely recommend! Review Title: Great, doesn't leave white cast Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: AllWell Beauty Masking Kit | Moisturizing Exfoliating Botanical Radiant Face and Body Mask | With Red Maple, Safflower, & Lavender | Made in the USA | Vegan, Cruelty-Free | 3.38 Fl Oz. Jar + Applicator (Self Care Kit) Review Date: 2022/04/08 Store: AllWell AllOver Average Rating: 3.5 Product Details: {'Brand': 'AllWell AllOver', 'Scent': 'Lavender', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Unit Count': '3.38 Ounce', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Product Dimensions': '5.25 x 4.25 x 4.13 inches; 12.31 Ounces', 'UPC': '850012824275'} Review Text: The product is very thick and doesn’t apply easy. It doesn’t really have a scent feels like mud. It starts drying quickly and starts flaking which causes a mess. The headband is not luxurious as described, its not soft either. I kept product on 20
Mins as it started falling off my face. My skin did feel very hydrated which is a plus. I will use it a few times a week as instructed but not sure I will purchase again. Review Title: Application is not great but mask is hydrating Rating: 4.0 --------------------------------------------------
